The mouth-watering presentations we see on ads on TV rarely resemble what we find at the these shops and Blossom shows us exactly how they achieve such. Even though we know that these ads are not realistic, these ads are mouthwatering and keep us coming back fro more. Some of the contents used in these ads will shock you. From the glue that's mixed with cheese to create that sticky cheese look on the pizza to seltzer tablets that make bubbles last longer in bubbly, these hack will leave you shocked. 